content.rendered:
Directed by Debamitra Biswal

Written by Meghvrat Singh

Cast Nawazuddin Siddiqui (Pushpinder Tyagi). Athiya Shetty (Anita ‘Ani’ Awasthi). Vibha Chhibber (Indu Tyagi). Karuna Pandey (Prabha – Ani’s Mausi). Bhumika Dube (Hema Tyagi (as Bhumika Dubey)). Navni Parihar (Mrs. Awasthi). Vivek Mishra (Kedar Awasthi). Abhishek Rawat (Haakim Tyagi). Sanjeev Vatsa (Manohar Tyagi (as Sanjeev Vats)). Usha Nagar (Pushpinder’s Daadi). Devansh Kumar (Ikka Tyagi). Medha Aich (Pushpinder’s Chachi). Sapna Sand (Pushpinder’s Aunt). Rahul Chelani (Devang- Pushpinder’s Friend). Vinod Surya (Sabziwala). Mustaqeem Shah (1st Groom). Braj Kishore Tiwari (1st Groom’s Father (as Brij Kishore)). Mamta Chopra (1st Groom’s Mother). Bishna Chouhan (Roli (as Bishna Chauhan)). Shailja Shukla (Roli’s Mother). Awadesh Kumar Shukla (Chillam Baba). Rachana Pakai (1st Bride). Shrikant Soni (1st Bride’s Father). Swastika Chakraborty (1st Bride’s Mother). Abhishek Rajput (1st Bride’s Brother). Dinesh Parihar (Band Wala). Praveen Ojha (Car Driver) . Deepak Rai (Collector peon)

Languages Hindi

Producers Syed Zaid Ali. Rajesh Bhatia. Rajesh Bhatia. Kiren Bhatiaa. Gayatri Gulati. Jitender. Shahid Mohd Qureshi. Asif Shaikh. Salim Shaikh. Kiran Zaveri
